title: Chopped After Hours S02E02 Family College Chicken WEB-DL.x264-JI
description:
Chopped After Hours - Season 2, Episode 2




After Hours Revisits Family, College and Chicken

Dough flies in round one as Geoffrey Zakarian races to reinvent the calzone and Maneet Chauhan accepts a lucrative bet from Ted Allen. Entrees get fratty in round two as Chris Santos indulges in collegiate amounts of cheese, while Marc Murphy shows his range by sinking pong shots across the kitchen. Marcus Samuelsson and Amanda Freitag manage to conjure up confections from poultry in round three, but Aaron Sanchez's toasted spices take the cake.




Original Air Date: 12-Jul-2016
